turns.userPrompt:
Build the tasks management feature:
- Backend API: GET /projects/:id/tasks, POST /tasks, PUT /tasks/:id, DELETE /tasks/:id
- Frontend: Project detail page showing tasks in a list/table
- Create task form (title, description, priority dropdown, due date picker)
- Inline task editing
- Task detail modal showing all information
- Filter tasks by status (All/Todo/In Progress/Done)
